  m_Name: The Cultural Organizer
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Character
  characterName: Cultural Organizer
  characterDescription: "You don't trust Enjin. You believe your own voice is more
    important than Enjin's voice. If Enjin is used, you want to understand why -
    Enjin needs to be a transparent tool.  \n\nThink about how you can maintain the
    identity of the company's employees. How can AI be made more transparent in the
    company? How much do you value data privacy? Get in character! \r\n"
